WEBVTT

00:07:29.996 --> 00:07:31.146
"So old."

00:07:36.795 --> 00:07:37.945
"So fast."

00:07:41.292 --> 00:07:44.902
I also got Mom to model
for my oil paintings.

00:07:45.942 --> 00:07:48.742
This painting is called "The Dressmaker."

00:07:50.101 --> 00:07:53.085
I remember, as a kid,

00:07:53.109 --> 00:07:55.823
Mom sewing clothes for the whole family

00:07:55.847 --> 00:07:59.364
on this massive, heavy sewing machine

00:07:59.388 --> 00:08:02.161
that was bolted
to the floor in the basement.